%h3 Addresses with significant differences in geocoded results

%table
  %thead
    %tr
      %th Address
      %th Average distance to average result (to nearest metre)
      %th Created
  %tbody
    - @queries.each do |query|
      %tr
        %td= link_to query.query, query
        %td= query.average_distance_to_average_result&.round
        %td
          = time_ago_in_words(query.created_at)
          ago
